The first thing I'm going to look at is I'm going to look at the Python extension that

00:07:16.839 --> 00:07:17.839
we built.

00:07:18.440 --> 00:07:20.799
Once I come in here, you'll see that I have a nice user interface that illustrates to

00:07:20.799 --> 00:07:25.480
Tableau users exactly what they need to do if they want to use this extension.

00:07:25.480 --> 00:07:29.160
There's also a nice feature for the developer which will allow me to come in here and test

